{"title":"母亲——写给故乡的椰子树","authors":["陈忠干"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":5,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写给故乡的椰子树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你披着青青的长发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望着蓝蓝的海峡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰子树呵椰子树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多象我久别的妈妈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，是在码头接船来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，是在等我回老家？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见你身影我心直跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少回——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中见到你老人家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上码头我情切切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多熟悉——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切的声音心里的话……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高瞻远瞩的老母亲呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔热情火辣辣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继承传统的好子弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总爱给这又给那！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身经百战的老母亲呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慷慨无私不掺假；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为党分忧的好儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管是对我还是对她！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们英雄的老一辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永记着，是你奶汁喂养大："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰碗盛椰水呵，喝饱又出发！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰浆拌椰丝呵，充饥把仗打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一喂喂了几十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘扬到天涯……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰子树呵老母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恩深如海怎报答？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如有人当官忘了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的历史定会惩罚他！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如有人长大不创业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的时代必将淘汰他！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又在长征呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为建设的儿女挡风沙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又在支前呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——让累累果实身上压……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}